snippet.title: Wakey Wakey
snippet.description:
Wishlist & Follow: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3047720/Wakey_Wakey/

A Puzzle Platformer about a sleepy guy...who just wants to get to Bed.

Moon Jam Games LLC & VoxPop Games, Inc. present...

Wakey Wakey is a Single-screen, 2D platforming game where the player needs to solve mysteries that are keeping you from a good night's rest.

You are sleeping....

Or at least trying to fall asleep

The world around is fill with WONDERS.

Find as many ways to get to sleep as possible.

Find as many outfits to fall asleep with.

Is it Morning already.....

WAKEY WAKEY
